Hi Amelia,

We're in the Jacksonville area and have a small unschooling group that meets weekly.? Contact me off list for more information.

Gail






-----Original Message-----
From: Amelia (Maria) Mallah <jasmizak@...>
To: unschoolingbasics@yahoogroups.com
Sent: Tue, 24 Feb 2009 2:07 pm
Subject: [unschoolingbasics] homeschoolers in northeast florida


























Hello everyone:

My children: Jasmine 13, John 10 and Jinan almost 5 just moved to

Anastasia Island, so we don't know any homeschoolers in the area. We

missed a lot all the nice moms and children we met in South Florida,one

of them is Christy Schultz from ECO, Cynthia, Kim, Delores, Dora,

Debbie and everybody else. Hope there are equally nice homeschoolers in

northeast Florida. Thank you,

Amelia
